  <div class="login-mobile-wrap">
    <div class="login-card">
      <h2 class="login-title">Privacy Policy</h2>
      <div class="privacy-text" style="white-space:normal;font-family:inherit;text-align:left;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;">
        <p>Effective date: December 19, 2025</p>
        <p>Spotizoom ("we", "us", or "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our website and services, in accordance with the laws of the United States, the European Union (GDPR), and other applicable jurisdictions.</p>
        <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><b>Account Data:</b> Name, email address, and optional social media profiles you provide.</li>
          <li><b>Usage Data:</b> IP address, browser type, device information, and usage statistics.</li>
          <li><b>Cookies:</b> We use cookies and similar technologies for authentication, security, and analytics.</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>To operate and maintain the Spotizoom platform and select daily winners.</li>
          <li>To communicate with you regarding your account or winnings.</li>
          <li>To improve our services and ensure security and fraud prevention.</li>
          <li>To comply with legal obligations.</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>3. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>We do <b>not</b> sell or rent your personal data.</li>
          <li>We may share data with service providers (e.g., email, hosting) under strict confidentiality agreements.</li>
          <li>We may disclose information if required by law or to protect our rights and users.</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>4. International Data Transfers</h3>
        <p>Your information may be processed in the United States and other countries. We implement safeguards to protect your data as required by applicable law, including the GDPR.</p>
        <h3>5. Data Retention</h3>
        <p>We retain your data only as long as necessary for the purposes described or as required by law. You may request deletion of your account and data at any time.</p>
        <h3>6. Your Rights</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><b>EU/EEA users:</b> You have the right to access, correct, delete, or restrict processing of your personal data, and to object to certain processing. Contact us to exercise your rights.</li>
          <li><b>California residents:</b> You have the right to know, delete, and opt out of the sale of personal information (we do not sell your data).</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>7. Children's Privacy</h3>
        <p>Spotizoom is not intended for children under 16. We do not knowingly collect data from children under 16.</p>
        <h3>8. Contact Us</h3>
        <p>If you have questions or wish to exercise your rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:spotizoom@gmail.com">spotizoom@gmail.com</a>.</p>
        <p>We may update this policy. Please review it periodically for changes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
